mothra vs. godzilla ( japanese : &lt;unk&gt; hepburn : gojira tai &lt;unk&gt; , lit . " counterattack " ) is a 1964 japanese tokusatsu kaiju film directed by tomoyuki fukuda . it is the fourth film in the godzilla series . it is the first film in the godzilla franchise . the film was produced by toho studios and distributed by tristar pictures .